            "title": "油價收市下跌",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">國際油價下跌，市場正評估美國對俄羅斯兩大石油公司的制裁，能否抵消全球供應過剩的隱憂。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250325_GL_source-AP_oil.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250325_GL_source-AP_oil.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">紐約期油報每桶61.5美元，跌29美仙，跌幅約0.5%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">倫敦布蘭特期油收市報每桶65.94美元，跌5美仙，跌幅近0.1%。</p>\n</div>",
