        {
            "title": "美股三大指數創新高   道指首逾47000點收市",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美股3大指數創即市及收市新高，道瓊斯工業平均指數首次於47000點以上收市。美國9月通脹數據溫和，減息預期增，加上企業業績表現理想，支持股市。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"美股 (AP圖片)\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/202508013_FI_source-ap_Financial_Markets_Wall_Street-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"美股 (AP圖片)\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/202508013_FI_source-ap_Financial_Markets_Wall_Street-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">美股 (AP圖片)</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">道指最多曾升逾590點，收市報47207點，升472點，升幅1%。高開76點後，升幅擴大至最多592點，高見47326點。</p>\n<!-- slider begin -->\n<div class=\"fancy-slider\">\n<p class=\"fancy-gallery-tips\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px; margin: 0\">點擊看圖輯</p>\n<div class=\"fancy-main\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"美股 (AP圖片)\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/202508013_FI_source-ap_Financial_Markets_Wall_Street-2.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"美股 (AP圖片)\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/202508013_FI_source-ap_Financial_Markets_Wall_Street-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">美股 (AP圖片)</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"資料圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/bplib_20230718-082645_20230718_GL_US-ECONOMY_fb_source-web__704px.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"資料圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/bplib_20230718-082645_20230718_GL_US-ECONOMY_fb_source-web__704px.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">資料圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1024x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250204_Google_source-ap.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1024x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250204_Google_source-ap.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"資料圖片\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/980x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/10/20251002_GL_apple-1.jpeg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"資料圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/980x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/10/20251002_GL_apple-1.jpeg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">資料圖片</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls-text bpcategory-special-color\">更多相片</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__buttons\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __prev fancy-main-prev\" style=\"border-right: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n<div class=\"rule\"></div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __next fancy-main-next\" style=\"border-left: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"美股 (AP圖片)\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/202508013_FI_source-ap_Financial_Markets_Wall_Street-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">美股 (AP圖片)</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"資料圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/bplib_20230718-082645_20230718_GL_US-ECONOMY_fb_source-web__704px.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">資料圖片</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1024x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250204_Google_source-ap.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">AP圖片</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"資料圖片\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/980x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/10/20251002_GL_apple-1.jpeg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">資料圖片</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- slider end -->\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">納斯達克指數報23204點，升263點，升幅1.15%。一度升1.39%，至23261點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">標準普爾500指數一度升穿6800點，收市報6791點，升53點，升幅近0.8%，曾揚1.02%，至6807點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">總結全星期，道指累升2.2%，納指和標普500指數分別升2.3%和1.9%，3項指數均連升兩星期。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"資料圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/bplib_20230718-082645_20230718_GL_US-ECONOMY_fb_source-web__704px.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"資料圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/bplib_20230718-082645_20230718_GL_US-ECONOMY_fb_source-web__704px.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">資料圖片</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美國9月消費物價指數按月上升0.3%，按年上升3%，均略低於市場預期。扣除食品及能源價格的核心指數，按月上升0.2%，按年上升3%，兩者均較8月數據回落。9月數據原定於本月中發布，但白宮表示，政府停擺導致數據暫停收集，10月通脹數據可能首次無法發布。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1024x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250204_Google_source-ap.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1024x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250204_Google_source-ap.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">IBM收市飆升7.9%，為表現最強道指成份股；Alphabet攀升2.7%，英偉達漲2.3%，超微半導體(AMD)急升7.6%；蘋果升1.3%，創收市歷史新高報262.82美元，本周累計升4.2%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">福特汽車上季盈利好過市場預期，股價急升逾12% ; 但Tesla跌逾3%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"資料圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/980x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/10/20251002_GL_apple-1.jpeg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"資料圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/980x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/10/20251002_GL_apple-1.jpeg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">資料圖片</p>\n</a>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15369769-%e7%be%8e%e8%82%a1%e4%b8%89%e5%a4%a7%e6%8c%87%e6%95%b8%e5%89%b5%e6%96%b0%e9%ab%98-%e9%81%93%e6%8c%87%e9%a6%96%e9%80%be47000%e9%bb%9e%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82",
